<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Marlborough</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The neighborhood was named after the city of Marlborough in England and offers all the modern amenities and conveniences that one could ask for. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">A majority of the homes for sale in Marlborough comprise of single-family detached homes and bungalows with a few apartment condominiums that have been developed only recently. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The average price of a typical suburban townhome in Marlborough is somewhere along the lines of $360,000. The residents enjoy easy access to a variety of shopping malls, libraries, playgrounds and schools in the neighborhood.</p>
        </div>
